  "title": "Sous Chef (2nd Chopper)  / 5 Days / Chinese Fine Dining",
  "description": "<p><strong>Chinese Fine Dining – Sous Chef (2nd Chopper)</strong><br /><strong>Working Hours:</strong> 44 hours per week<br /><strong>Work Days:</strong> 5 days work, 2 off days - Split Shift<br /><strong>Meals:</strong> Provided<br /><strong>Location:</strong> North Bridge Road<br /><strong>Nearest MRT:</strong> Bras Basah / City Hall</p><h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><ul><li><p>Assist with menu planning, inventory control, and portion management</p></li><li><p>Reduce food waste through proper storage and efficient usage of ingredients</p></li><li><p>Maintain consistent food quality and production standards</p></li><li><p>Follow and enforce kitchen SOPs and procedures</p></li><li><p>Ensure high standards of food safety, hygiene, and cleanliness</p></li><li><p>Ensure safe and proper use of kitchen equipment and guide team members</p></li><li><p>Perform other duties as assigned by the Reporting Manager</p></li></ul></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li>Kitchen experience, preferably in Cantonese or Chinese cuisine</li><li>Able to handle fast-paced kitchen environment</li><li>Good teamwork and communication skills</li></ul><p>If you are interested, please send your resume to <strong>lucas.chang@swiftsearchglobal.com</strong> or whatsapp/call - <strong>9339 2324</strong></p><p>EA Personnel Name: Lucas Chang<br />EA Personnel No: R1874043<br />EA License No: 18C9495</p>",
